<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222" /><cite id="CITEREFGauss1823" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Carl_Friedrich_Gauss" title="Carl Friedrich Gauss">Gauss, C. F.</a> (1823). "Theoria Combinationis Observationum Erroribus Minimis Obnoxiae, Pars Prior". <i>Commentationes Societatis Regiae Scientiarum Gottingensis Recentiores</i>. <b>5</b>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Commentationes+Societatis+Regiae+Scientiarum+Gottingensis+Recentiores&amp;rft.atitle=Theoria+Combinationis+Observationum+Erroribus+Minimis+Obnoxiae%2C+Pars+Prior&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.date=1823&amp;rft.aulast=Gauss&amp;rft.aufirst=C.+F.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AUnimodality" class="Z3988"></span></span>
