<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222" /><cite id="CITEREFD._F._Vysochanskij,_Y._I._Petunin1980" class="citation journal cs1">D. F. Vysochanskij, Y. I. Petunin (1980). "Justification of the 3σ rule for unimodal distributions". <i>Theory of Probability and Mathematical Statistics</i>. <b>21</b>: <span class="nowrap">25–</span>36.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Theory+of+Probability+and+Mathematical+Statistics&amp;rft.atitle=Justification+of+the+3%CF%83+rule+for+unimodal+distributions&amp;rft.volume=21&amp;rft.pages=25-36&amp;rft.date=1980&amp;rft.au=D.+F.+Vysochanskij%2C+Y.+I.+Petunin&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AUnimodality" class="Z3988"></span></span>
